               <msContents>
                  <summary>Image of the Archangel Mika’el, ሰላም፡ ለከ፡ ሚካኤል፡; Image of Gabriel, መልክአ፡ ገብርኤል፡; Image of Saint George zä-Säläda Mogäs, መልክአ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ዘሰሌዳ፡ ሞገስ፡; Hymn to Saint George, “O who is quick for help,” ኦ፡ ፍጡነ፡ ረድኤት፡</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>

                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="17v" facs="005">Fols 1r–17v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2835RepCh119">Malkǝʾa
                                                  Mikāʾel</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ስምከ፡ ምስለ፡ ስመ፡ ልዑል፡ ዘተሳተፈ፡</incipit>
                  </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="17v" to="27r" facs="022">Fols 17v–27r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2965RepCh246">Malkǝʾa
                                                  Gabrǝʾel</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላመ፡ ገብርኤል፡ መልአክ፡ በላዕለ፡ ማርያም፡ ዘአዕረፈ፡</incipit>
                  </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <locus from="27v" to="44v" facs="032">Fols 27v–44v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2866RepCh147">Malkǝʾ-hymn to St
                                                  George</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምከ፡ ዘሰሌዳ፡ ሞገስ፡ መጽሐፉ፡</incipit>
                  </msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <locus from="44v" to="46r" facs="024">Fols 44v–46r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3100RepCh380">Malkǝʾa
                                                  Giyorgis</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ኦ፡ ፍጡነ፡ ረድኤት፡ ለጽኑዕ፡ ወለድኩም፡</incipit>
                  </msItem>

